Package com.strongjoshua.console

Class GUIConsole

java.lang.Object
com.strongjoshua.console.AbstractConsole
com.strongjoshua.console.GUIConsole
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Disposable, Console
public class GUIConsole extends AbstractConsole
A simple console that allows live logging, and live execution of methods, from within an application. Please see the GitHub Repository for more information.

    • GUIConsole

      public GUIConsole()
      Creates the console using the default skin.
      ***IMPORTANT*** Call Console.dispose() to make your InputProcessor the default processor again (this console uses a multiplexer to circumvent it).
      Default key toggle is apostrophe: '
      See Also:
      • Console.dispose()
